{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport_chain-1.0/DASH-up_transport_chain-icon.svg", "type": "node", "context": "vop", "internal": "up_transport_chain", "version": "1.0", "namespace": "DASH"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Up Transport Chain"], "extent": [49, 72]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Parallel Transport Frame operation done in sequence."], "extent": [72, 133]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [133, 148], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Similar to ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport-1.0", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport-1.0.html"}, " VOP, where an initial Up vector is transported along the many input Forwards."], "extent": [148, 273]}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "inputs", "container": true, "type": "inputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [273, 281], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["forwards"]}], "extent": [281, 294], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Array for forward directions throughout which the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Initial Up"]}, " will be transported."], "extent": [294, 389]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "text": "Inputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [389, 401], "body": [{"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Transport"], "extent": [401, 418], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Initial Up"], "extent": [418, 431], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Up direction two be transported over the multiple Forwards."], "extent": [448, 513]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "prev_up"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Average Forward"], "extent": [513, 530], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Uses an average of previous and the next forward on each iteration. If using tangents form ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/orientalongcurve", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/orientalongcurve.html"}, ", its best to set its ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Tangent Type"]}, " parameter to ", {"type": "em", "text": ["Next Edge"]}, ", if this is to be used."], "extent": [551, 761]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 4, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport_chain-1.0/DASH-up_transport-help_average_forward.svg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [761, 830], "body": [], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "half left"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "average_fwd"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Method Bias"], "extent": [863, 876], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["There are two methods to solve the up transport; one produces one more perpedicular to both forwards, the other, one more coplanar to both forwards and this method blends between them."], "extent": [897, 1086]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 4, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport_chain-1.0/DASH-up_transport-help_method_bias.png", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [1086, 1151], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 8, "text": ["Progression of a vertical direction, {0,1,0}, transported multiple times with different values of Method Bias."], "extent": [1179, 1305]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "wide left"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "method_bias"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Alignment"], "extent": [1305, 1321], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The transported up vector can also be aligned to an explicit direction or an auto-banking direction, based on the curvature between the forward directions."], "extent": [1321, 1479]}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Align Amount"], "extent": [1479, 1493], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["How much should be the new up vector be transformed to either align to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Target Direction"]}, " or the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Bank Direction"]}, "."], "extent": [1508, 1632]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "align"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Align Angle Limit"], "extent": [1632, 1651], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["This avoids the alignment rotation to go above a specific angle value. This parameter\u2019s UI is in degrees, more human-friendly, but the input port connection expects values in radians, more trigonometry-friendly. Be aware of these differences."], "extent": [1672, 1920]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "align_limit"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Align Target/Bank Bias"], "extent": [1920, 1944], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["At ", {"type": "code", "text": ["0"]}, " the alignment will be totally to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Target Direction"]}, ", while at ", {"type": "code", "text": ["1"]}, " the alignment will be totally towards the auto-banking."], "extent": [1968, 2104]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "align_dir_bias"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Target Direction"], "extent": [2104, 2122], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Direction to align the transported up vector towards, while still being perpedicular to forward."], "extent": [2142, 2244]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "target_dir"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Target As Line"], "extent": [2244, 2260], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["When the target direction would require, for example, a 135\u00ba rotation, activating this will instead only require a -45\u00ba rotation, a shorter rotation, keeping the current up more stable."], "extent": [2281, 2471]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 4, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport_chain-1.0/DASH-up_transport-help_target_as_line.svg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [2471, 2539], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 8, "text": ["With Target as Line activated the shortest rotation to line direction, not vector, will be picked."], "extent": [2567, 2681]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "wide left"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "target_line"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Bank In/Out Direction"], "extent": [2681, 2704], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["When auto-banking this determines if the alignment will be towards the inside or outside of the curve, or even the closest perpendicular direction."], "extent": [2722, 2874]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 4, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/nodes/vop/DASH--up_transport_chain-1.0/DASH-up_transport-help_bank_direction.svg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [2874, 2942], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 8, "text": ["Bank towards the inside of the curve at 0.0, towards outside at 1.0, and towards the closest perpedicular direction at 0.5 ."], "extent": [2970, 3110]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "wide left"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "bank_dir"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Array Auto Resize"], "extent": [3110, 3136], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Common Size"], "extent": [3136, 3149], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 2, "text": ["Determines the size that all input arrays will have. ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Min"]}, " will use the smallest array\u2019s size, while ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Max"]}, " will use the greatest array\u2019s size.\n  For this particular asset only the Forwards input is taken into consideration for this."], "extent": [3178, 3418]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "array_autoresize_size"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Fill"], "extent": [3418, 3424], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 2, "text": ["Sized up arrays need a fill value. This determines whether the fill is the parameter\u2019s ", {"type": "em", "text": ["Default"]}, " or, if the array is not empty, its ", {"type": "em", "text": ["Last"]}, " or ", {"type": "em", "text": ["First"]}, " value.\n  For this particular asset only the Forwards is not resized."], "extent": [3453, 3675]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "array_autoresize_fill"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 3, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "extent": [3675, 3685], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Description"], "extent": [3685, 3698], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 2, "text": ["String to display info on top of the node in the network view. The pilcrow \u00b6 button enables multi-line text."], "extent": [3717, 3830]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "description"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}]}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "outputs", "container": true, "type": "outputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [3830, 3839], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["ups"]}], "extent": [3839, 3847], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Transported up vectors."], "extent": [3858, 3887]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "up"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["fwds"]}], "extent": [3887, 3895], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Used forward vectors. Affected by ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Average Forward"]}, "."], "extent": [3907, 3967]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "fwd"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["tforms"]}], "extent": [3967, 3977], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["3\u00d73 Matrices created from ", {"type": "ui", "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["fwds"]}]}, " and ", {"type": "ui", "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["ups"]}]}, "."], "extent": [3991, 4048]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "tform"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["cases"]}], "extent": [4048, 4057], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Code value reporting the validity of the inputs or special cases of the operation."], "extent": [4071, 4158]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["-2"]}, ": Both Forwards have zero length. Output ", {"type": "ui", "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["up"]}]}, " is just a copy of the input."], "extent": [4158, 4247]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["-1"]}, ": Previous Up vector has zero length. Output ", {"type": "ui", "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["up"]}]}, " is just a copy of the input, zero."], "extent": [4247, 4346]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": [" 0"]}, ": Up and Forwards directions are all valid. Not zero lengths."], "extent": [4346, 4418]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": [" 1"]}, ": Both Forwards are colinear, pointing in the same or in opposite directions."], "extent": [4418, 4506]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": [" 2"]}, ": Up vector is colinear to Next Forward."], "extent": [4506, 4557]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": [" 3"]}, ": Both ", {"type": "code", "text": ["1"]}, " and ", {"type": "code", "text": ["2"]}, " cases."], "extent": [4557, 4593]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": [" 4"]}, ": Previous Forward has zero length."], "extent": [4593, 4639]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": [" 5"]}, ": Next Forward has zero length."], "extent": [4639, 4686]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "cases"}}], "container": true}, {"type": "load_example_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "load_example", "indent": 0, "text": [" Up Transport"], "role": "item", "extent": [4686, 4714], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Example scene for this asset."], "extent": [4765, 4799]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"examplefile": "/demos/vop/up_transport_demo.hda"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Outputs"}], "title": ["Up Transport Chain"], "summary": ["Parallel Transport Frame operation done in sequence."]}